114
00:08:20,941 --> 00:08:22,769
Muž v čiernej taške...

115
00:08:22,770 --> 00:08:24,616
- Čierna...
- Ticho.

116
00:08:27,741 --> 00:08:30,230
Prečo ste nič nepovedali?

117
00:08:30,511 --> 00:08:32,897
