130
00:09:05,020 --> 00:09:06,305
<i>Philip, ste v nebezpečenstve.</i>

131
00:09:06,520 --> 00:09:08,389
<i>Musíme sa stretnúť.</i>

132
00:09:08,390 --> 00:09:10,019
